item.title: 【HD Live Performances】HDTV - Carly Rae Jepsen - Summer Sonic Festival, Japan, 2015 [1080p]
item.description:
This is a 7 songs recording, highly recommended if you love Carly. I assembled it from 2 different recordings which happened to have exactly the same quality.

The first one had Run Away With Me, Gimmie Love, Emotion, Your Type, I Really Like You. The second one had All That, Call Me Maybe, I Really Like You.

I removed I Really Like You from the first recording and kept it from the second one. Then I joined both files with MKV Toolnix and I added chapters for each song. All operations were lossless, so the quality remained intact.

Setlist:
1. Run Away With Me
2. Gimmie Love
3. Emotion
4. Your Type
5. All That
6. Call Me Maybe
7. I Really Like You
